title: Boredom
author: Monerd22
pages:
#- While this is only one poem, I have put a great deal of effort in making it, as I have only recently started writing poems. I will aim to put at least two poems in my books when I am more comfortable writing them. I hope you enjoy it.§0
§0          -Monerd22
#- 
